M	1	2002-06-09	2	1	1	7
F	2	2002-06-09	3	3	1	7
F	3	2002-06-09	4	4	1	7
F	4	2002-06-09	5	5	1	7
F	4	2002-06-09	6	5	1	7
M	5	2002-06-09	7	7	1	7
